stylometry: Data mining is the analyzing of extensive data collected.  Data mining can be used to collect consumer buying trends.  This is why large companies like Giant Eagle, CVS, Costco, etc have these membership cards that give the consumer deals and money off gas.  This allows the company to track what each person buys, what day, what time, what they buy, and what they buy with it.  That is data mining . Taking the information from each consumer storing it in a data warehouse which is then later analyized to help the company maximize profit or revenue or cut cost.
